### Summary

My input code works fine in the gameview, but does not function in sceneview. Even though I click on the scene to make it active, the input is not functioning.
### How to reproduce [Bugs]

Attach the 2 scripts below to a gameobject, and place it above a platform (Anything that has a rigidbody set to static on it, allowing collisions)

